{"tid":2160100,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"梁啟智：泛民議員辦事處的職員，份工係支援在囚手足，叫人總辭嘅人係咪安排好晒呢班職員份糧？","createTime":"2020-08-16T17:46:44.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-17T17:58:20.000Z","uid":50275,"like":43,"dislike":57,"uniUserReply":69,"replies":[{"pid":"d7a11041cc06d5ca9ec0fea49c85f3734cd18b90","tid":2160100,"uid":50275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-16T17:46:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>講開又講，我識好幾個議員辦事處的職員，份工實際上係支援在囚手足，一日到黑唔係去探監、陪家屬上法庭，就係去寄物資。我有條比較實際的問題：那些正在高叫總辭，將道德純潔放第一位嘅政治人物，係咪已經安排好晒呢班職員份糧？係就出聲，大家少樣嘢顧慮。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2020/08/17/4RXkcP.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2020%2F08%2F17%2F4RXkcP.png&h=5686e78e&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"ddd723bd276aec3ab87f202d2ab02026771cfe91","tid":2160100,"uid":50275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-16T17:47:28.000Z","msg":"？"},{"pid":"ca3657938ec56ff828a3c7e81731fcf49649a88d","tid":2160100,"uid":15356,"like":41,"dislike":43,"score":-2,"citedBy":7,"replyTime":"2020-08-16T17:49:32.000Z","msg":"講嚟講去咪又係為咗份人工"},{"pid":"e6ec60c0ccfcb1d3e085da27a49b2f1b020f5aee","tid":2160100,"uid":92340,"like":56,"dislike":8,"score":48,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-08-16T17:50:22.000Z","msg":"咁講法，冇人應該出去抗爭，老實講，邊個冇負擔？<br />\n大把人連前途都冇埋"},{"pid":"b2d9958b19cf04d30d2be2d341b7b19f8c65bfdd","tid":2160100,"uid":66784,"like":32,"dislike":5,"score":27,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-16T17:52:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>探監、陪家屬上法庭，就係去寄物資。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n呢啲只係好小事，攞黎做反對總辭嘅理由，會唔會薄弱咗啲？"},{"pid":"e0fce3840bef88fdb516d094db3c0bd3b68146c8","tid":2160100,"uid":98016,"like":46,"dislike":7,"score":39,"quote":{"pid":"ca3657938ec56ff828a3c7e81731fcf49649a88d","tid":2160100,"uid":15356,"like":41,"dislike":43,"score":-2,"citedBy":7,"replyTime":"2020-08-16T17:49:32.000Z","msg":"講嚟講去咪又係為咗份人工"},"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-08-16T17:52:18.000Z","msg":"探監，陪上庭，準備文件，<br />\n真係要請人做，<br />\n無左人工，就真係無左人手，<br />\n其實好現實"},{"pid":"f0